{"type": "article", "id": 23944, "title": "茶叶包装做成这样，也许不爱茶的人都想试试", "description": "从外到里传递一种轻松的感觉，而不仅仅是所谓的“高级”。", "date": "2016-03-16T11:35:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3441, "name": "茶叶包装"}, {"id": 24973, "name": "Tea branding"}], "category": 17, "author": 403280, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 370, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703120220PYtFwMj7fq6pEGiA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">不知道你有没有在便利店见过这样的茶棒（Tea stick），比起一般的茶包，茶棒通过表面的孔洞让热水充分进入内部循环，又不至于像茶包一样吸水性过强，茶叶一般都因为浸泡拥挤在一起。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120214uHKOzprvgxC1MSBt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120214zp914F8iP6BKHhdu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75694444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>最近，一家叫 Typical Organization 的工作室有了新作品，他们帮希腊茶叶品牌 Elixir tea 的茶棒做了包装。Typical Organization 很好地利用了茶棒的孔状特点，包装的表面分布有网状的小波点，以及将茶棒泡在杯中的扁平化形象。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031202145NbUZDpiFnPO3CHu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81527778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">随着茶叶的承载体渐渐有所细分，人们在包装上做的努力也开始有了很明确的划分。像 Elixir tea 的这款包装显然更有现代感。</p>\n<p class=\"\">我们为你整理了几个好看的茶叶包装，来看看针对不同的茶艺表现，设计公司会做出怎样的解读：</p>\n<h2>草本茶品牌 Ecokavkaz   </h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120215subPzNqf4MTSc3VD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120215BZIVJDFieTW1ksYX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71805556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">设计者：Unicorn Studio Moscow   </div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">白底纯色包装代表纯草本茶。</p>\n<p class=\"\">黑底混合包装代表混合茶叶（草本茶，绿茶/红茶茶叶）</p>\n<p class=\"\">包装主体是一个花纹复杂的装饰性 logo，但用最单一的色彩填充。给今后品牌的口味衍生预留了可能性。</p>\n<h2>El Greco</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312021623JiTEztDSG7MwfA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120216uwFOoM2h1T5Ace6C.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">设计者：twomatch!</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">希腊除了海滩、日光和巨大的湛蓝天空，也有山脉和植被覆盖，茶叶和草本植物就是其中一种。</p>\n<p class=\"\">包装上的三角形用简单的线条勾勒出山脉的地形，又用不同色系将 8 种口味的茶区分开。</p>\n<h2>Simply Tea</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120216tEzoXbRmWKhIdy07.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98194444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031202170MHyYuUtJ7W19v2E.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">首席设计: <a href=\"http://www.magharl.co.uk/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Magnet Harlequin</a>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">联合设计: <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/thomasmonsen\">Thomas Monsen</a></p></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Simply Tea 单纯只以大包装形式出售给餐饮业，但设计师仍然认为品牌的调性很重要，于是就有了迷宫花纹和相当成熟的配色。</p>\n<h1>Stassen Teas</h1>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120217AbXF0kMGdHrZ1Cev.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120218phFDKaMq6NuC2TBR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">设计者: <a href=\"http://brandingbygarden.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Branding by Garden</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">相比之下，斯里兰卡的 Stassen 包装就相当具有本土风情和辨识度，这家建于 1977 年的老牌茶叶公司做的是纯正的锡兰红茶。</p>\n<h2>Zen Tea</h2>\n<p><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120218Tu2zf7kSvUO3DExG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61527778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120218NFqJO6x487lMZK0D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">设计者：<a href=\"http://konradsybilski.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Konrad Sybilski</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">一款极简主义包装，想传达宁静和谐的情绪。</p>\n<h1>Opal Tea Co.</h1>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120219YOixzmCXRy5cjApW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120219EFMTzJmU4yVGOrjw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">设计者：<a href=\"http://www.ha-ru.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Haruko Hayakawa</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">花茶。在色彩表达上更加丰富。图案由舒展的茶叶拼成，代表了高品质的茶艺。</p>\n<p class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://retaildesignblog.net/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">retaildesignblog</a></p>\n\n"}